        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer355364749" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8981638350050555990">Taken as a novel, lots of fun. Taken as a historical novel, lots of &quot;huh?&quot;. Key facts from the life of the real Lucrezia Borgia are omitted, dates are rearranged, and events central to the telling of Scarsbrook&apos;s story veer so far from the known record, that it&apos;s sometimes a leap to stay in the narrative. Enjoy the tale, but don&apos;t take it as the gospel truth. </span>
  <span id="freeText8981638350050555990" style="display:none">Taken as a novel, lots of fun. Taken as a historical novel, lots of "huh?". Key facts from the life of the real Lucrezia Borgia are omitted, dates are rearranged, and events central to the telling of Scarsbrook's story veer so far from the known record, that it's sometimes a leap to stay in the narrative. Enjoy the tale, but don't take it as the gospel truth. </span>
  <a data-text-id="8981638350050555990" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
